            </persName>
            <birth when="c.1730"/>
            <death when="1795"/>
            <note>The son of a Welsh miner, Williams was a mining engineer with forty years' experience. He worked in various locations in Scotland; in 1789 published The Natural History of the Mineral Kingdom. Died in Italy where he was carrying out further researches. </note>
         </person>
